"```sql\nSELECT s.MailStreet, s.School\nFROM satscores ss\nJOIN schools s ON ss.cds = s.CDSCode\nWHERE ss.AvgScrRead = (\n    SELECT MIN(AvgScrRead)\n    FROM satscores\n);\n```\n\nThis SQL query joins the `satscores` table with the `schools` table using the foreign key relationship between `satscores.cds` and `schools.CDSCode`. It selects the mailing street address and the school name for the school with the lowest average reading score."